FWIW, I have rolled through the full 2^32 SP space to make sure every float maps to exactly the same value as the reference implementation (and we implement float-to-int similarly in the codegen). For DP, this is infeasible, but I let it run overnight with random bit patterns.

But I have added more tests around large values as requested just to make sure.

